cff-version: 1.2.0
title: PyTex
message: "If you use PyTex, please cite the software and the scientific references documented in the repository."
type: software
license: GPL-3.0-or-later
authors:
  - family-names: PyTex contributors
repository-code: "https://github.com/kvmani/pytex"
abstract: >-
  PyTex is a pure-Python-first library for crystallographic texture and diffraction
  with a canonical data model, LaTeX-first scientific documentation, and MTEX-plus validation goals.
